<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<title>Email OTP Verification</title>
<style>
  body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: #f7f9fc;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 540px;
    background: #ffffff;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  .header h2 {
    text-align: center;
    color: #00a63d;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .message {
    color: #444;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .otp-box {
    margin: 20px auto;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    background: #e8f8ee;
    border: 2px dashed #00a63d;
    font-size: 26px;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: bold;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    width: fit-content;
  }
  .footer {
    margin-top: 25px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #888;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>üîê Verify Your OTP</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="message">
      <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
      <p>Your verification code is below. Please use this OTP to complete your login/verification:</p>
      <div class="otp-box">{{otp}}</div>
      <p>This code will expire in <strong>10 minutes</strong>.</p>
      <p>If you did not request this, you can ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; 2025 Hasan. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>